value.0: They destroyed my home and everything I love... Can you help me get my revenge?
The Byysk... Out by the old crypt.
One Hundred... Please.
Have you killed them all yet?
Have you killed them all yet?
Thank you... Do you think you could kill another One Hundred?
Have you dealt with that lot?
Have you dealt with that lot?
Thank you... Is it possible to do another One Hundred?
Back already? You've killed them?
Back already? You've killed them?
You really are my hero...
Do you think... You can kill One Thousand of them?
You're back? Did you kill all One Thousand already?
You're back? Did you kill all One Thousand already?
You-... You're right... I'm sorry... Here, please take this.
You're right... Thank you
Hello! Thank you for your help! I've put an ad on the holonet for work here on Hutlar as a support person to others that have lost their lives to Byysk, and it seems i'm not the only one.
No, I don't do revenge.
Sure... Who is they?
Sure, how many are we talking?
I'll be back soon.
Not yet, no.
Yes I have.
No... One hundred was enough.
Another One Hundred... Sure.
No... It's a lot of Byysk.
Yes. Another One hundred dealt with.
Are you serious? No... Two hundred is enough.
... Since they destroyed your home, I'll help you...
Not yet...
Yes... Yes I have. Another One Hundred have been dealt with.
Is there anything else I can do for you?
You have got to be joking. No. I am done.
... Fine. But this better be worth my time.
No, i'm still working on it.
No... No I did not. I killed another One Hundred, and I stopped. I'm done. Four Hundred Byysk is enough.
Look.. I'm sorry you lost your home and family, but there has to be a better way to express how you feel.
Good luck, Sharene.
I'm glad to hear it, Sharene. Good luck with your future.
